    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1869-12-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1869-12-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="310" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d310">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName>,
                                    Secretary of State, to Mr. <persName type="to">Roberts</persName>, Spanish minister.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of
                                        State</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-12-08">
                        <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 8,
                                1869</date>.</dateline>
                <p>The undersigned, Secretary of State of the United States, has the
                                honor to transmit to Mr. Lopez Roberts a copy of a note of the 5th
                                instant, which he has received from Mr. Freyre, the minister of
                                Peru, conveying his assent, on behalf of his government, to the
                                departure of the gun-boats constructed for the Spanish government by
                                Mr. Delamater, of New York; also a copy of the reply thereto by the
                                undersigned.</p>
                <p>The undersigned offers to Mr. Lopez Roberts on this occasion renewed
                                assurances of his highest consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>HAMILTON FISH.</item>
                            <item>Señor Don <hi rend="smallcaps">M. Lopez
                                            Roberts</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
